screen_desc: The screenshot shows an Amazon app interface with a map and details for an Amazon Locker location. The search bar at the top contains the address "412 Warren St, Schenectady, New York 123". Below the map, the recommended Amazon Locker location is "Amazon Locker - Fely" at 93 W Campbell Rd, at Via Port Rotterdam Mall, Schenectady, NY, 12306-6800. The operating hours are Mon-Sat: 11am - 7pm and Sun: 11am - 6pm. There is a note that the Amazon App is needed to open the locker, with a link to learn how it works. There is also an option to add this location to the address book. The bottom navigation bar includes icons for home, video, account, cart, and menu.
